naughty /ˈnɔːtɪ/

(naughtier,naughtiest) 

1. ADJ If you say that a child is naughty , you mean that they behave badly or do not do what they are told. 淘气 

例： Girls, you're being very naughty. 姑娘们，你们太调皮了。 

2. ADJ You can describe books, pictures, or words as naughty when they are slightly vulgar or related to sex. 下流的 

例： You know what little boys are like with naughty words. 你知道小男孩们说下流话是什么样子。

